import * as React from "react";
import ListItemIcon from "@mui/material/ListItemIcon";
import ListItemText from "@mui/material/ListItemText";
import AccessTimeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AccessTime';
import ListItemButton from '@mui/material/ListItemButton';
import InsertEmoticonIcon from '@mui/icons-material/InsertEmoticon';import Divider from "@mui/material/Divider";
import ThumbUpIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ThumbUp';
import CalendarTodayIcon from '@mui/icons-material/CalendarToday';
import TranslateIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Translate';
import LiveTvIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LiveTv';
import RemoveRedEyeIcon from '@mui/icons-material/RemoveRedEye';
import ExplicitIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Explicit';
import TheaterComedyIcon from '@mui/icons-material/TheaterComedy';
import Rating from '@mui/material/Rating';
import {YearSlider} from "./Sliders"


function SideMenuItems(props) {
    const [yearOpen, setYearOpen] = React.useState(false);
    const handleClick = (event) => {
      setYearOpen(!yearOpen)
    };
  return(
    <React.Fragment>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <TheaterComedyIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Critic Score" />
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <InsertEmoticonIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="User Score" />
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <CalendarTodayIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Release Year"/>
      </ListItemButton>
      <Divider sx={{ my: 1 }} />
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <ThumbUpIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Genre"/>
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <ExplicitIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Rating" />
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton 
        onClick={handleClick(yearOpen, setYearOpen)}
      >
        <ListItemIcon>
          <CalendarTodayIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Release Year"/>
      </ListItemButton>
      {props.open && yearOpen?<YearSlider/>:<></>}
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <TranslateIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Langugae"/>
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <AccessTimeIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Runtime"/>
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <LiveTvIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Streaming"/>
      </ListItemButton>
      <ListItemButton>
        <ListItemIcon>
          <RemoveRedEyeIcon/>
        </ListItemIcon>
        <ListItemText primary="Seen it"/>
      </ListItemButton>
    </React.Fragment>
  );
  }
  
  export default SideMenuItems;
